    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Temporibus Heinrici regis filii quondam Heinrici
                        imperatoris anno decimo, die vigesima prima mensis marcii, indic(ione)
                        quarta, <placeName ref="#places/594">RAV(enne)</placeName>. Fecit cartam <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">enfit(eosis)</rs> domnus <persName
                            key="#Monks"><name ref="Wido Pomposianus">Wido</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monachus</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/1460"><placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Pomposie</placeName></orgName>, ad firmandam ab
                            <rs key="#Abbots">abbate</rs> ipsius monasterii cum consensu aliorum
                        monachorum, <persName><name ref="Petrus de Walterio">Petro de
                            Waltero</name></persName> pro se et pro <persName><name ref="Walterius"
                                >Waltero</name></persName> avunculo suo eorumque filiis et nepotibus
                        de omnibus rebus illis, quas detinet <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes de Teutio">Iohannes de Teucio</name></persName> iure
                        suprascripti monasterii, positas in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis" ref="#places/4606">Campus
                            Domnicus</placeName>, <rs key="#Fines">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/3513" key="#Fines"><geogName ref="#estates/2424"
                                key="#Fines">Faventino</geogName></placeName>, <rs key="#Plebs"
                            >plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/1490">Sancti Iohannis in
                                <placeName ref="#places/3527">Axiata</placeName></orgName>. Et
                        call(ciarium) inde recepit <rs key="#Price">den(ariorum) Veron(ensium) libras decem</rs>,
                        eo
                        tenore si intra totum mensem madii ipse aut abbas suprascripti monasterii
                        sive alii rectores persolverint predictas libras prenominatis petitoribus
                        aut suprascriptorum heredibus, ipsi debebunt recipere absque omni alio
                        lucro, et si intra totum mensem madii non persolverint, deinde in antea
                        debebunt habere omnes fructus et redditus illius terre donec illis sit
                        persolutum totum suprascriptum deditum.</ab>
